{"tid":1448831,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場","createTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:25:29.000Z","uid":55155,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7b3309c935a2762779566782c075a62fa7bb70f0","tid":1448831,"uid":55155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:07.000Z","msg":"一人一 狂洗連登post [時事台]<br />\n唔該你出一份力，肯出post，聽日就係人都知入機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 標題：「警察還眼」明天1PM全民入機場 百萬人塞爆機場<br />\n<br />\n無時間文宣<br />\n見POST者，自行Copy開新Post，要連登全部都係呢個Post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n812起 1PM，有人性既你立刻罷工，百萬人進入機場，咩都唔做，勢要討回雙眼<br />\n機場因為100萬人係機場而暫停運作，不是們的責任，是因為機場不夠大<br />\n圍到出青馬，都全條橋唔夠闊<br />\n<br />\n統一口號，兩句，要入健力士，等歷史知道<br />\n「黑警還眼」<br />\n「五大訴求，缺一不可」<br />\n<br />\n黑警聽住：<br />\n一係你就入機場殺哂所有人<br />\n一係你就還返隻眼出黎<br />\n否則百萬人不離開機場<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大群：<a href=\"https://t.me/airport730\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fairport730&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=7394e4b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/airport730</a><br />\n實時Channel: <a href=\"https://t.me/hk730air\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhk730air&d=4tZOiqwfeINLG3hE5eaPvE6%2B9elrQwgXj79VqWXxFjk%3D&h=a8af09fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hk730air</a>"},{"pid":"fd1e827e9df4bf4d81235dee3f0e026b6173e52f","tid":1448831,"uid":55155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1fad6c4e2129a4472244c75e6f1bec7acd8ca938","tid":1448831,"uid":55155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:41:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62c3a30e7763e0fbc995badcb6c1e497471f98c3","tid":1448831,"uid":55155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29280863856f56a4f27520e47278f2c4226bbaff","tid":1448831,"uid":171326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T16:42:11.000Z","msg":"721"},{